LOGGER_ENV =  provide the environment type (development or production)  

OTEL_EXPORTER_TRACE_ENDPOINT = provide the url for exporting traces ( http://localhost:4000/v1/traces ) 

OTEL_EXPORTER_LOG_ENDPOINT =  provide the url for exporting logs (http://localhost:4000/v1/logs)

OTEL_EXPORTER_METRICS_ENDPOINT = provide the url for exporting metrics (http://localhost:4000/v1/metrics)